[[Image:Necronomicon (game by Fairy Tale).png|thumb|right|200px|Screenshot of Necronomicon by Fairy Tale]]
{{nihongo|'''''Necronomicon'''''|ネクロノミコン}} is an adult-themed, horror-[[adventure game]] set in the town of [[Arkham]] in [[H. P. Lovecraft]]'s fictional world.  The story included [[Deep Ones]] and hybrid spawn-folk.  Fairytale (Hardcover) was the publisher.

The game was released on the [[NEC PC-9801]] and the [[Fujitsu]] [[FM Towns]] Japan-market computers in 1994.

The FM Towns version of the game included a [[Red Book (audio CD standard)|CDDA]] orchestral soundtrack; some tracks with synthesized "horror" effects and opera-style singing.

